HEADWORD: Nonmalignant
<hw>Non`ma*lig"nant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not malignant,
as a disease; -- used especially of tumors; <as>as, a
<ex>nonmalignant</ex> growth on the liver</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
